  "prompt": "What hotel in Gorakhpur would be safe for unmarried couples, without the harassment of police, hotel staff, and moral police?",
  "response": "Finding a hotel where unmarried couples can stay without facing harassment is indeed important for a comfortable and enjoyable experience. While specific policies and attitudes can vary, here are a few general tips to increase the likelihood of a smooth experience:\n\n1. **Reputable Chains**: Opt for well-known hotel chains that have clear policies regarding guests.\n2. **Online Reviews**: Check online reviews and travel forums for feedback from other unmarried couples.\n3. **Booking Platforms**: Use booking platforms like OYO, MakeMyTrip, or Goibibo which often have filters or mentions of couple-friendly hotels.\n4. **Direct Confirmation**: Call the hotel directly ahead of time to confirm their policies on unmarried couples.\n\nIn Gorakhpur, here are some hotels reputed to be couple-friendly:\n\n1. **Hotel Clarks Inn Grand**\n2. **Hotel Ganesh**\n3. **Hotel Kama International**\n\nPlease ensure you carry valid ID proofs and any necessary documentation, as compliance with local laws and policies are essential in any hotel stay.",
